Vibify - A Spotify Playback Controller
Requirements:
Windows OS

Internet connection

Spotify account

Spotify app running (on your PC or another device)

How to Use:
Download Vibify.exe and save it to a folder (e.g., Desktop).

Double-click Vibify.exe to launch the app.

A browser window will openâ€”log in with your Spotify account.

Close the browser tab after seeing "Login Complete!"

Start playing a track in Spotify, and Vibify will display the track info.

Use the buttons to control playback (play, pause, skip, etc.).

